OOC: Predacons in Black Aracnia's group are to ignore Inferno731 because as 
of now his actions do not count on my ship. If he dosent want to help me he 
needs to leave the ship or return to power. He dosent post enough so we could 
reslove this problem. I dont want it taking a week to settle this, but he 
NEVER posts! Sorry Inferno, but I have to do this.

    Aracnia looked at Quickstrike and Darkmouse, "Its in vector 9.84-1. when 
you find it report to me immedietly. I want to know what that thing is." She 
said.

    Megatron looked at Drillbot. "Of course I know what your doing! Im trying 
to keep you on your toes and alert! After all, I have so many troops coming 
and going its hard to remember whos who! Now hurry and program that pod! I 
have to deal with the dinobot."
